00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:02,000
Tong Liu.

239
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:02,000
Hao Xiao.

240
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:08,560
Li Zhang.

241
00:12:08,560 --> 00:12:09,560
Li Zhang.

242
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:10,090
Li Zhang.

