00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:20,280
Liu Wang.

244
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:20,480
Jia Ningrao Jiaying Xidou Rong.

245
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:21,400
Jia Ningtao Jia.

